attachments.title: 5369 W Donges Ln, Brown Deer, WI 53223 | MLS #1626806 | Zillow
attachments.text: For sale: $319,000. Stunning 4 bedroom 3.5 bath contemporary in one of the prettiest neighborhoods of Brown Deer. Impressive foyer with dramatic cathedral ceilings complemented by the open floor plan.Great Room, Mud Room, Office, Kitchen,DR, Music Room or Den, and three generous bedrooms make up the first floor. The lower level has another large bedroom, Bath, Laundry and a wonderful Rec Room with wet bar and built ins. Beautiful Yard and patio. Everything you could want nestled in a quiet little corner of Brown Deer.
